<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bn">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>MD AMIR ALI | Photography</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:wght@700&family=Inter:wght@400;500;600&display=swap');
        
        :root {
            --primary: #e11d48;
        }
        
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            background-color: #0a0a0a;
            color: #e5e5e5;
            line-height: 1.6;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }
        
        header {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            width: 100%;
            background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.95);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            z-index: 1000;
            padding: 1.2rem 5%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--primary);
            letter-spacing: 2px;
        }
        
        nav a {
            color: #ccc;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-left: 2rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: color 0.3s;
        }
        
        nav a:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
        }
        
        .hero {
            height: 100vh;
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.7), rgba(0,0,0,0.8)), url('https://picsum.photos/id/1015/1920/1080') center/cover no-repeat;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            position: relative;
        }
        
        .hero-content {
            max-width: 800px;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }
        
        .hero h1 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 4.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .hero p {
            font-size: 1.4rem;
            color: #ddd;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: white;
            padding: 14px 40px;
            border-radius: 50px;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            transition: all 0.4s;
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            background: #f43f5e;
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        
        section {
            padding: 100px 5%;
        }
        
        h2 {
            font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
            font-size: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            color: #fff;
        }
        
        .gallery {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
        }
        
        .gallery img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 350px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 12px;
            transition: transform 0.5s, box-shadow 0.5s;
        }
        
        .gallery img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(225, 29, 72, 0.3);
        }
        
        .about {
            background: #111;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .about p {
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 0 auto 2rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #bbb;
        }
        
        .contact {
            background: #0a0a0a;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px;
            background: #000;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            color: #666;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; }
            nav a { margin-left: 1rem; font-size: 0.95rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="logo">MD AMIR ALI</div>
        <nav>
            <a href="#gallery">গ্যালারি</a>
            <a href="#about">আমার সম্পর্কে</a>
            <a href="#contact">যোগাযোগ</a>
        </nav>
    </header>

    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>MD AMIR ALI</h1>
            <p>আলোকচিত্রশিল্পী | গল্প বলি আলো ও ছায়া দিয়ে</p>
            <a href="#gallery" class="btn">আমার কাজ দেখুন</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="gallery">
        <h2>নির্বাচিত কাজ</h2>
        <div class="gallery">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/1015/800/600" alt="Photography 1">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/201/800/600" alt="Photography 2">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/237/800/600" alt="Photography 3">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/1016/800/600" alt="Photography 4">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/133/800/600" alt="Photography 5">
            <img src="https://picsum.photos/id/180/800/600" alt="Photography 6">
        </div>
    </section>

    <section id="about" class="about">
        <h2>আমার সম্পর্কে</h2>
        <p>আমি এমডি আমির আলি, একজন প্যাশনেট ফটোগ্রাফার। প্রকৃতি, মানুষ এবং শহুরে জীবনের অদ্ভুত সৌন্দর্যকে ক্যামেরায় ধরে রাখতে ভালোবাসি।</p>
        <p>প্রতিটি ছবির পেছনে একটা গল্প থাকে — আমি সেই গল্পগুলোকে আলো, ছায়া ও মুহূর্তের মাধ্যমে তুলে ধরি।</p>
    </section>

    <section id="contact" class="contact">
        <h2>যোগাযোগ করুন</h2>
        <p>নতুন প্রজেক্ট, শুটিং বা কোনো কথা বলতে চাইলে নিচে মেসেজ করুন।</p>
        <p style="margin: 30px 0; font-size: 1.3rem;">
            📧 <strong>amirali172009@gmail.com</strong><br>
            📱 +880 XXXXXXXXXX
        </p>
        <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" class="btn">Instagram-এ ফলো করুন</a>
    </section>

    <footer>
        &copy; 2026 MD AMIR ALI Photography. All Rights Reserved.<br>
        Made with ❤️ using GitHub Pages
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
